<h2>How to Request Data Deletion</h2>
<p>You have the right to request the deletion of your personal data stored in the Desco Lead CRM system. We take data privacy seriously and will process your request promptly.</p>

<div class="info-card highlight">
  <h4><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Submit a Data Deletion Request</h4>
  <p>Send an email to:</p>
  <p style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary-light); margin: 12px 0;">
    <a href="mailto:shokirovsharifjon04@gmail.com">shokirovsharifjon04@gmail.com</a>
  </p>
  <p>Include the following in your email:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Subject line: <strong>"Data Deletion Request"</strong></li>
    <li>Your full name (as submitted in the lead form)</li>
    <li>Your phone number or email address (for identification)</li>
    <li>A description of what data you want deleted</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<h2>Deletion Process</h2>

<div class="data-flow">
  <div class="data-flow-step"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Step 1: Submit Request via Email</div>
  <div class="data-flow-arrow"><i class="fas fa-arrow-down"></i></div>
  <div class="data-flow-step"><i class="fas fa-search"></i> Step 2: Identity Verification (1-3 days)</div>
  <div class="data-flow-arrow"><i class="fas fa-arrow-down"></i></div>
  <div class="data-flow-step"><i class="fas fa-database"></i> Step 3: Data Located & Reviewed</div>
  <div class="data-flow-arrow"><i class="fas fa-arrow-down"></i></div>
  <div class="data-flow-step"><i class="fas fa-trash-alt"></i> Step 4: Data Permanently Deleted</div>
  <div class="data-flow-arrow"><i class="fas fa-arrow-down"></i></div>
  <div class="data-flow-step"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Step 5: Confirmation Email Sent</div>
</div>

<h2>What Data Will Be Deleted</h2>
<p>Upon a valid deletion request, we will permanently remove:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Your name, phone number, and email from our Client database</li>
  <li>Any associated Deal/Lead records</li>
  <li>Activity logs related to your records</li>
  <li>Any notes or comments containing your personal information</li>
</ul>

<h2>Response Time</h2>
<div class="info-card">
  <h4><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Processing Timeline</h4>
  <p>We will acknowledge your request within <strong>3 business days</strong> and complete the deletion within <strong>30 calendar days</strong>.</p>
  <p>You will receive a confirmation email once your data has been permanently deleted from all our systems.</p>
</div>

<h2>Important Notes</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Data deletion is <strong>permanent and irreversible</strong>. Once deleted, we cannot recover your data.</li>
  <li>We may retain certain data if required by law or for legitimate legal purposes.</li>
  <li>Aggregated, anonymized data that cannot identify you may be retained for analytics.</li>
  <li>If you submitted a lead through Facebook/Instagram, you may also want to manage your data directly through <a href="https://www.facebook.com/settings" target="_blank">Facebook Settings</a>.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Facebook Data Deletion Callback</h2>
<p>As required by Meta Platform Terms, we support the Facebook Data Deletion Request callback. When you remove our app from your Facebook settings, we receive a notification and automatically initiate the data deletion process.</p>

<div class="info-card highlight">
  <h4><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Need Help?</h4>
  <p>If you have any questions about the data deletion process, please contact us at <a href="mailto:shokirovsharifjon04@gmail.com">shokirovsharifjon04@gmail.com</a>.</p>
</div>
